title: Dreamkillers first 3 eps
description: The first three releases from Brisbane loud/fast/heavy band The Dreamkillers. I don't know how well known they were outside of Brisbane but in their home town they were nothing short of absolute legends. Their live shows were a blast and always something to look forward to. Their music was hmmm.... I guess a mixture of metal,punk,hardcore,thrash with a dash of whatever thrown in. These recordings are long out of print and I guess original copies are quite rare. For those who were looking for these in that other torrent... enjoy.
